welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Bongaree, Australia! Get ready to experience the laid-back charm of this coastal town known for its stunning beaches and relaxed atmosphere. Enjoy your stay and explore all that Bongaree has to offer!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Caloundra Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is used for private and charter flights at Caloundra Airport.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: International Terminal
terminals.description: The international terminal at Brisbane International Airport serves as the primary gateway for international flights to and from Australia.

terminals.name: Domestic Terminal
terminals.description: The domestic terminal at Brisbane International Airport handles all domestic flights within Australia.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport, but limited to 3 hours per device per day.
